# Cheat Sheet

  Command                            Purpose
  ---------------------------------- ---------------------------------------
  `sudo ufw status`                  Display firewall status
  `sudo ufw status verbose`          Display detailed firewall information
  `sudo ufw enable`                  Enable the firewall
  `sudo ufw disable`                 Disable the firewall
  `sudo ufw allow 80/tcp`            Allow HTTP
  `sudo ufw allow OpenSSH`           Allow SSH using application profile
  `sudo ufw deny 8080/tcp`           Block a TCP port
  `sudo ufw delete allow 8080/tcp`   Remove a firewall rule
  `sudo ufw status numbered`         Display numbered rules
  `sudo ufw app list`                List available application profiles

